{"tid":339110,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[免費BITCOIN] 水龍頭推薦討論區","createTime":"2017-07-28T18:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T06:31:22.000Z","uid":107274,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fdf05acd13545765cbaa9868811c3e0b2d061879","tid":339110,"uid":107274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:14:53.000Z","msg":"BITCOIN價格由15新年起暴升，漲到依家USD2,700一個，開始穩定番<br />\n升得咁勁令不少人留意BITCOIN<br />\n<br />\n如果新手的你，不知道BITCOIN是什麼的話，可以睇下呢個POST係其他玩BITCOIN 既巴打整出黎比大家了解一下BITCOIN<br />\n<br />\nBitcoin/ Ethereum 加密貨幣新手入門（4）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/317230/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/317230/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n<br />\n=====================================================<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">WALLET</div></span><br />\n<br />\n一開波玩水龍頭瘋狂開帳號係少不免<br />\nWALLET 更加係玩BITCOIN前最重要開既帳號<br />\n因為你拎錢點都要有個地址先比到錢你<br />\n所以WALLET 點都要至少開1個<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blockchain.info/wallet/#/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblockchain.info%2Fwallet%2F%23%2F&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=5c95bbb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://blockchain.info/wallet/#/</a><br />\n<br />\nBLOCKCHAIN 呢個wallet 勝在介面好 同埋可以同手機APP同步<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bitoex.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bitoex.com%2F&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=278c5e8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bitoex.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣WALLET 可以放BITCOIN 之餘 更可以連番銀行帳戶payout cash<br />\n但係你要有台灣銀行account 先做到 但係勝在有中文同BITCOIN走勢<br />\n更加緊貼BITCOIN 同埋BitoEX 係可以買BITCOIN 的<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://coinpot.co/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcoinpot.co%2F&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=1a1cdfa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://coinpot.co/</a><br />\n<br />\nCoinPot 唔算係一個WALLET 但係佢同好多水龍頭都有連繫 <br />\n好似bonus bitcoin, moon bitcoin, bit fun <br />\n所以申請埋係無錯, 佢係夠5萬satoshi先可以唔洗fee 轉番入wallet<br />\n<br />\n個人就唔建議用Xapo<br />\n因為Xapo近期出咗新的收費方法，發送比特幣回私人錢包，手續費高達23萬satoshi，收取比特幣回Xapo錢包也同樣要收費，費用高到相當婊，所以若非比特幣大戶，請不要再使用此錢包。<br />\n<br />\n=====================================================<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Bitcoin Faucet</div></span><br />\n<br />\nFreebitco<br />\n<br />\n最大最信得過既faucet<br />\n每個鐘可以係1-10000抽一個數字，再比返對應既Bitcoin你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://sonzim.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/nhan-bitcoin-mien-phi-tren-freebitcoin-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsonzim.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fnhan-bitcoin-mien-phi-tren-freebitcoin-2.png&h=d26deef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次抽完之後可以得到2張樂透券參加每週抽獎，<br />\n樂透抽獎獎勵會依照目前參加抽獎的人次逐漸累計上去。<br />\n<br />\n夠30000 satoshi就可以withdraw去自己wallet<br />\n<br />\n如果巴打用我條LINK比我做介紹人，我有設定每期結算會依據您抽獎的活動紀錄返傭50%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/014328_9f6f882d735ab6b00b7a5d826e299cba.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F014328_9f6f882d735ab6b00b7a5d826e299cba.JPG&h=f999a74e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/d8vE84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fd8vE84&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a23cb86a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/d8vE84</a><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n以下係CoinPot 有連繫的水龍頭，Claim完就直接入落CoinPot到<br />\n而CoinPot係夠5萬satoshi就可以withdraw去自己wallet<br />\n<br />\nBonus Bitcoin<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bonusbitcoin.co/img/logo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbonusbitcoin.co%2Fimg%2Flogo.png&h=278b89ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同FreeBitcoin差唔多，好處係每15分鐘禁一次，每次平均有60幾Satoshi<br />\n要係claim下邊有個按鈕係Change your claim settings<br />\n到set番Always receive the average claim amount<br />\n咁就可以每15分鐘拎current average通常都係60 Satoshi<br />\n佢好就好在有5% Daily Bonus，都係勤力D就拎多D<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/YZZEu9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FYZZEu9&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d93843d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/YZZEu9</a><br />\n<br />\nMoon bitcoin<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-hlf1AyjUgv0/WXJJOFvQz1I/AAAAAAAADyg/lLHEqJ4vCycaelZzzaFydfabehxE1gHTACKgBGAs/s320/moonbitcoin.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-hlf1AyjUgv0%2FWXJJOFvQz1I%2FAAAAAAAADyg%2FlLHEqJ4vCycaelZzzaFydfabehxE1gHTACKgBGAs%2Fs320%2Fmoonbitcoin.jpg&h=286f6812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最快5分鐘禁一次，同樣唔洗狂禁，會幫你儲住直一到你CLAIM為止，個人覺得派得唔算多，而且都係派去CoinPot先，網頁不用長開也能累積比特幣，隔一陣禁下都儲起左40幾50 Sat。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/zSMZkL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FzSMZkL&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=0cdc7e77\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/zSMZkL</a><br />\n<br />\nBitFun<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bitfun.co/img/logo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbitfun.co%2Fimg%2Flogo.png&h=482789d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要累積超過3分鐘就可以直接領取，同樣唔洗狂禁，會幫你儲住直一到你CLAIM為止，而且都係派去CoinPot先，網頁不用長開也能累積比特幣，但實際測試過當你累積越多時每分鐘累積的比特幣就會越少，所以建議半小時收一次喔！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/DL9VVp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FDL9VVp&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=69b4870e\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/DL9VVp</a><br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n以下係睇廣告賺Bitcoin的水龍頭<br />\n<br />\nAdbtc<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/BIXWmK5Aswc/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FBIXWmK5Aswc%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=24ead0a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠15000 satoshi就可以withdraw去自己wallet<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/GPi5jt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FGPi5jt&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=54c54941\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/GPi5jt</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTC Clicks<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://k60.kn3.net/taringa/1/3/9/4/6/C/PlayrunYt/1B5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fk60.kn3.net%2Ftaringa%2F1%2F3%2F9%2F4%2F6%2FC%2FPlayrunYt%2F1B5.png&h=b436ab95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠10000 satoshi就可以withdraw去自己wallet<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/ZfZNhK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZfZNhK&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=17ca1da5\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/ZfZNhK</a>"},{"pid":"ca918d461573373d1bd73e0e93ac70f186a2b8e2","tid":339110,"uid":107274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:18:54.000Z","msg":"以下係慢慢等佢收息的水龍頭<br />\n<br />\nBitminer<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bitminer.io/s/l1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbitminer.io%2Fs%2Fl1.png&h=f3b7cf12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢係一個入左wallet 之後慢慢等佢去到50萬satoshi就可以withdraw<br />\n可以話係一個夠哂懶同方便的水龍頭<br />\n比起什麼雲端miner，同用自己電腦miner都好得多<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/9m7amc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F9m7amc&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=feae32d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/9m7amc</a><br />\n<br />\nStartminer<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i6.imageban.ru/out/2017/03/16/83bedd5a8ed4800d8aecd0276c3dcfc5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi6.imageban.ru%2Fout%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F83bedd5a8ed4800d8aecd0276c3dcfc5.png&h=6f58e61d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同bitminer一樣都係慢慢等佢去到50萬satoshi就可以withdraw<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/7rm7WL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F7rm7WL&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a4bbb55f\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/7rm7WL</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n以上係小弟平時用開拎bitcoin的水龍頭，如果其他巴打有好用的可以推薦一下<br />\n而網址都是有推薦CODE的，我會全部都set做同註冊的巴打50%分<br />\n如果不想用我的網址登記也可以，希望大家接受BITCOIN水龍頭的資訊而且"},{"pid":"a9106a3eca3d92f162f0e3540d92cb94283946cd","tid":339110,"uid":81167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:29:26.000Z","msg":"Btcclicks 係幾好，感覺上賺得比其它快，以下係我條referral link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://btcclicks.com/?r=49748ea9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbtcclicks.com%2F%3Fr%3D49748ea9&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=99d3baaf\" target=\"_blank\">http://btcclicks.com/?r=49748ea9</a>"},{"pid":"70f1153aff68f28cd5305d2b19d403803348db38","tid":339110,"uid":17704,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:16:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁撚多scam仲想呃人做你下線？</span></span>"},{"pid":"0d9b00dcc5eb37a5732e4bf39b1af01f375a0f26","tid":339110,"uid":107251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁撚多scam仲想呃人做你下線？</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係 樓主想賺都笑喎 <br />\n<br />\n求其買1蚊bitcoin 收下息算啦 <br />\n免費野要搞咁多野 搵鬼玩"},{"pid":"65e2b501756764a006ff03013808481e3b658c27","tid":339110,"uid":107274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:41:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁撚多scam仲想呃人做你下線？</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係 樓主想賺都笑喎 <br />\n<br />\n求其買1蚊bitcoin 收下息算啦 <br />\n免費野要搞咁多野 搵鬼玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<